Subject: $9M rollout/Compucom- BigDeals: 46190798 v.34, cust. CHRISTIANA CARE
BodyText:
Hi HP Friends, Compucom is shopping this deal, approx $9M rollout. D&H has been very aggressive lately on HPI.
We typically sell at zero mark up and give them 1% b/e rebate and net 60. I put the parts in a quote above for you at our current standard pricing.

We will go in as aggressively as possible but worried we won't win. Do you have any funds to help us secure the deal?

From Brian below:
All ship to Paulsboro, also as you know this is bid out to other disty.  The first 1300 of the 800 mini's are definitely getting ordered from DH as they are the only with stock at the moment.

Please let us know, thanks!!

Carolyn Wylie
Sales Supervisor, National Accounts



TD SYNNEX - Clearwater
5350 Tech Data Drive
Clearwater, FL 33760 
(800) 237-8931 x4001821
Carolyn.Wylie@tdsynnex.com
CompuCom@tdsynnex.com

"ANY PRICING INFORMATION INCLUDED HEREIN IS FOR QUOTATION PURPOSES ONLY AND IS NOT AN ORDER OR OFFER TO SELL.  ALL PRICES AND DESCRIPTIONS ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE WITHOUT NOTICE.  ALL PRODUCTS ARE SUBJECT TO AVAILABILITY FROM THE MANUFACTURER"
